Usage: placeInstance [-help] <inst> <location>
                     [{R0 R90 R180 R270 MX MX90 MY MY90}] [{ -fixed  | -placed  | -softFixed  }]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<inst>                                 # instance name ((inst), required)
<location>                             # coordinate of new origin
                                       # (point, required)
{R0 R90 R180 R270 MX MX90 MY MY90}     # new orientation (enum, optional)
-fixed                                 # mark instance as fixed
                                       # (bool, optional)
-placed                                # mark instance as placed
                                       # (bool, optional)
-softFixed                             # mark instance as softFixed
                                       # (bool, optional)